NexPoint and Highland – The Value of Experience




The Value Of Experience


NexPoint Capital is a healthcare focused business development company sponsored by NexPoint Advisors, an affiliate of Highland Capital Management, L.P.
Founded in 1993 to focus on credit and alternative investments, Highland Capital Management, L.P. and its affiliate advisors (together “Highland”) is an institutional investment firm with approximately $13.4 billion of capital under management and a particular expertise in the healthcare sector.  Highland provides the strategic investment expertise that guides NexPoint Capital.
We believe our specialized expertise affords us the ability to identify the “winners” and to provide NexPoint Capital investors with a unique opportunity to benefit from the ongoing strength and historic change in the quickly evolving healthcare sector.
