Jul 14 17
The board of directors of NexPoint Capital, Inc. declared a cash distribution of $0.013846 per share of the company’s common stock, par value $0.001 per share, to be paid on August 30, 2017, to the stockholders of record on August 7, 2017, August 14, 2017, August 21, 2017, and August 28, 2017.


NexPoint Capital, Inc. Declares Cash Distribution, Payable on August 2, 2017
Jun 5 17
On June 2, 2017, the board of directors of NexPoint Capital, Inc. declared a cash distribution of $0.013846 per share of the company’s common stock, par value $0.001 per share, to be paid on August 2, 2017, to the stockholders of record on July 3, 2017, July 10, 2017, July 17, 2017, July 24, 2017, and July 31, 2017. Based on the Company’s current public offering price of $10.50 per share, the distribution represents an annualized rate of approximately 6.9%.


